metadata.name: Zvezdny Peak
metadata.description:
Zvezdny peak is the highest point of the Ergak range (2265 m). It is a treacherous and dangerous mountain with steep walls. 

Before I photographed it, the mountains were covered with thick fog. But after a while the sunlight broke through the shroud and the wind showed the top. 

Everything inside froze at the sight of such a sight. I had only a few seconds to capture it before the fog cleared completely.

Location Ergaki National Park, Siberia
